You get an error because a label cannot be applied to variable declarations, that&#39;s just how [the language grammar][1] is defined (a label can only precede a `Statement`, and a `LocalVariableDeclarationStatement` is not a `Statement`). The reason is probably that it could cause confusion concerning variable scope. This works:

