To add to Michael Borgwardt&#39;s answer, you can do things like this for convenience (I just discovered this the other day while reading through the Java rt.jar source code):

    BlockSegment:
    if (conditionIsTrue) {
        doSomeProcessing ();
        if (resultOfProcessingIsFalse()) break BlockSegment;
        otherwiseDoSomeMoreProcessing();
        // These lines get skipped if the break statement
        // above gets executed
